表的代码预览取药

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('get') and o.name = 'FK_GET_GET_COLLECTO')
alter table get
drop constraint FK_GET_GET_COLLECTO
go

if exists (select 1
from sys.sysreferences r join sys.sysobjects o on (o.id = r.constid and o.type = 'F')
where r.fkeyid = object_id('get') and o.name = 'FK_GET_GET2_MEDICINE')
alter table get
drop constraint FK_GET_GET2_MEDICINE
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('get')
and name = 'get2_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index get.get2_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysindexes
where id = object_id('get')
and name = 'get_FK'
and indid > 0
and indid < 255)
drop index get.get_FK
go

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('get')
and type = 'U')
drop table get
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: get */
/*==============================================================*/
create table get (
cno char(8) not null,
mno char(10) not null,
constraint PK_GET primary key nonclustered (cno, mno)
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: get_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index get_FK on get (
cno ASC
)
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: get2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index get2_FK on get (
mno ASC
)
go

alter table get
add constraint FK_GET_GET_COLLECTO foreign key (cno)
references collector (cno)
go

alter table get
add constraint FK_GET_GET2_MEDICINE foreign key (mno)
references medicine (mno)
go
